sequenceDiagram
    participant L as ./spectro desktop
    participant E as Electron main.ts
    participant JVM as spectro-server.jar
    participant Win as BrowserWindow
    L->>L: stop stale instance (single-instance lock)
    L->>L: gradlew :spectro-server:bootJar
    L->>E: npm start (JAVA_HOME/bin on PATH, .env loaded)
    E->>E: findFreePort()
    E->>JVM: spawn java -jar spectro-server.jar --server.port=P
    loop up to 30 s, every 500 ms
        E->>JVM: GET /api/health
    end
    JVM-->>E: 200 {"status":"ok"}
    E->>Win: loadURL(http://127.0.0.1:P)
    Note over E,JVM: window close keeps app + JVM alive (tray, cron)<br/>Quit: SIGTERM, after 5 s SIGKILL
